<h2><br/>
Mediterranean School of Complex Networks 2023</h2>
<p>Catania, Sicily 25 – 30 June 2023</p>
<p>In the last decade, network theory has been revealed to be a perfect instrument to model the structure of complex systems and the dynamical process they are involved into. The wide variety of applications to social sciences, technological networks, biology, transportation and economic, to cite just only some of them, showed that network theory is suitable to provide new insights into many problems.<br/>Given the success of the Seventh Edition in 2022 of the Mediterranean School of Complex Networks, we call for applications to the Eighth Edition in 2023.</p>
<p>More at: <a href="https://mediterraneanschoolcomplex.net/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">mediterraneanschoolcomplex.net</a></p>
